Name: P30-39
checklistText:
Pre Thrust Targeting
    30 - External Delta V
        Sequence of Events:
            V37E30E
            Flashing V06 N33
                Ground Elapsed Time of Ignition (TIG)
                    00XXX. hours
                    000XX. minutes
                    0XX.XX seconds
            V25E to load desired TIG.
            PRO
            Flashing V06 N81
                Impulsive Delta V at TIG in Local Vertical Coordinates
                    X XXXX.X
                    Y XXXX.X
                    Z XXXX.X
            V25E to load desired Delta V.
            PRO
            Flashing V06 N81
                Apogee/Apolune Altitude XXXX.X nmi
                Perigee/Perilune Altitude XXXX.X nmi
                Magnitude of Delta V at TlG XXXX.X nmi
            PRO
            Flashing V16 N45
                Mark Counter (VHF-Optics) XXbXX marks
                Time from Ignition (TFI) XXbXX min/s
                Middle Gimbal Angle at TIG with Vehicle +X Axis in Direction of Thrust XXX.XX deg
                If the REFSMMAT flag is reset (that is, the IMU is not aligned) MGA (R3) will equal -00002.
            PRO
            V37E 00E
